&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project Executive – Lead Strategic Projects at Dome Construction&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a seasoned construction leader ready to take on a high-impact role? At &lt;strong&gt;Dome Construction&lt;/strong&gt;, we’re seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Project Executive&lt;/strong&gt; to oversee complex projects, drive client relationships, and shape the future of our business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Project Executive, you’ll work at the intersection of project delivery and strategic leadership—guiding teams, managing budgets, and ensuring client satisfaction. You’ll also play a key role in business development, talent management, and maintaining Dome’s reputation for excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary client representative, building trust and ensuring project success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee project teams, providing mentorship, training, and resource allocation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage budgets, schedules, and risk mitigation strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead client feedback initiatives and implement continuous improvement measures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive business development efforts, industry networking, and proposal strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of construction management experience, with proven leadership in complex projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+ years of direct client engagement for business development and preconstruction services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of local construction industry professionals and market trends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional communication, leadership, and problem-solving skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to travel up to 50% of the time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join Dome?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Influence strategic decisions and shape the future of our projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with top-tier clients and industry leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enjoy a culture built on integrity, safety, and continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive compensation and comprehensive benefits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ready to lead with impact? Apply today and help us build lasting relationships and exceptional projects.&lt;/p&gt;
