&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be part of a team that values integrity, innovation, and excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work on diverse, high-impact projects across California.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enjoy opportunities for growth, mentorship, and career advancement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary and comprehensive benefits package.&lt;/li&gt;
